{"tid":1396263,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"現在正式徵用黑洞作為任務台","createTime":"2019-08-02T04:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T05:56:41.000Z","uid":42691,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"02f6d6af67d6e005be7bf26c2cf60c77ba981dac","tid":1396263,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:44:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>現況</ins></strong><br />\n吹水台太多post  容易沉底<br />\n導致好多任務類型既post要不斷自推<br />\n浪費好多手足既時間<br />\n而想幫手做任務既巴打又遇唔到呢類post<br />\n結果有心做既冇得做 想做既遇唔到<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>提議</ins></strong><br />\n將部份任務類型post 開係黑洞<br />\n好似打機咁 黑洞就係你既任務清單<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">現在正式徵用黑洞作為任務台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>任務類型舉例</ins></strong><br />\n1.[聯署]禁對港售武<br />\n2.[檢舉]檢舉fb點相post<br />\n3.[推post]幫手推呢個post<br />\n4.[要人]馬鞍山要人<br />\n5.[登報]急求兩個排版手足<br />\n6.[尋片]求昨晚所有一手片<br />\n7.[投訴]三個步驟投訴tbb<br />\n8.[起底]幫手起xxx 有任何資料 發送到此新電郵<br />\n9.[夾錢]登報/手術費&hellip;<br />\n10. ..............<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>注意事項</ins></strong><br />\n1.黑洞內只會有任務列表<br />\n盡量不作任何討論 一旦陷入討論 就要追post <br />\n追追下就冇人想做 <br />\n2.係其他台討論完 整理好先入黑洞開post<br />\n3.未整理好既post 麻煩幫手負皮<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">想巴絲幫手做任務 就清楚列明任務要求 \n唔好入到去先傾先研究\n記住內文越簡潔清楚 越少討論 越方便巴絲做任務\n甚至部份任務可以俾非會員做</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>最後</ins></strong><br />\n每做完一個 左手邊就會有紅點 <br />\n未做就誠實消除回帶<br />\n可以大概統計你為香港做咗幾多貢獻<br />\n加上我發現巴絲開始有懶散跡象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望呢個任務清單台可以鼓勵多d人做任務<br />\n要懶既 贏咗再慢慢懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輸咗既話 我地將會活在地獄 永不超生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b116749b7b12a744b2ee8a456ff30f6bceb924","tid":1396263,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"同意 資訊討論行動貼既混集<br />\n令人混亂 更加容易令人懶散"},{"pid":"37f4affe2aa6c253e52cd3fbee5a09683753218e","tid":1396263,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:13:27.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a14ce46e5465e0d303bd37aef7484a6dfcc79e","tid":1396263,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:23:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da15800536627bafc15be8a162572a8a6d7df190","tid":1396263,"uid":215322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:26:01.000Z","msg":"覺得可以"},{"pid":"dbd6945a8ec311bb4446060d7bd7debc26c5ef1e","tid":1396263,"uid":215322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2990ca164de5aac3ac1dbc0df6a765ada78494","tid":1396263,"uid":277540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"都好呀  尋日我巳覺亂 追POST 都浪費晒D時間  無心機追POST  無晒時間了解作戰同文宣"},{"pid":"caeeb79ad059346460685de6020cb234698b1b90","tid":1396263,"uid":277540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:27:56.000Z","msg":"TG 又係開9咁多個都唔知點跟 唉.."},{"pid":"cd8d1c039ec91e80f412a5383aafa949d8f5c2ed","tid":1396263,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:44:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7dde3a42f3e7bf31a21d92bf43348cd92b3da95","tid":1396263,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:47:33.000Z","msg":"大家幫手整理下現有既任務 開去黑洞！！"},{"pid":"7b956acb1ef7b71d8b22ff61db523da5f0168aee","tid":1396263,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:51:09.000Z","msg":"你咪on9啦 係都活動台啦"},{"pid":"b1c9bdbc7a4551bdc417014c42c414c2fa00cb8a","tid":1396263,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b956acb1ef7b71d8b22ff61db523da5f0168aee","tid":1396263,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:51:09.000Z","msg":"你咪on9啦 係都活動台啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:56:41.000Z","msg":"好 都得 各有各做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連仔可唔可以開放黑洞</span></span>"}]}